opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiffs motion to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is denied for failure to comply with, the provisions of Supreme Court Rule 28.
BEVILACQUA, C. J., and DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Norman E. V. D’Andrea, F. Thomas O’Halloran, Providence, for plaintiff.
Anthony De Simone, Providence, for defendant.

William SOUSA v. Paul HANOIAN.
No. 78-381-Appeal.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
Nov. 29, 1979.
Norman E. V. D’Andrea, F. Thomas O’Halloran, Providence, for plaintiff.
Anthony De Simone, Providence, for defendant.
